Élodie Chérie https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/%C3%89lodie_Ch%C3%A9rie 0 Élodie Chérie (born 9 September 1969) is the stage name of a French former pornographic actress and model. Born in Saint-Étienne, in 1996 Chérie received the Hot d'Or for best supporting actress for her performance in La Princesse et la pute. Outside her career in adult industry, she was spokesperson of "Magics Fans", the association of supporters of AS Saint-Étienne.
